@startmindmap
<style>
mindmapDiagram {
  BackgroundColor transparent
  node {
    BackgroundColor #ffffff
    BorderColor #e7e0d8
    BorderThickness 1.2
    FontName Arial
    FontSize 11
    FontColor #3d3530
    RoundCorner 7
    Padding 5
    Margin 3
  }
  rootNode {
    BackgroundColor #c2620a
    BorderColor #a0510a
    FontColor #ffffff
    FontName Arial
    FontSize 13
    FontStyle bold
    Padding 10
    RoundCorner 10
  }
  arrow {
    LineColor #d1c4b8
    LineThickness 1.5
  }
  leafNode {
    BackgroundColor #fffcf8
    BorderColor #e7e0d8
    FontSize 10
    FontColor #78716c
    Padding 4
    Margin 2
  }
  .foundational {
    BackgroundColor #fef3e8
    BorderColor #c2620a
    FontColor #7a3a0a
    FontStyle bold
  }
  .patching {
    BackgroundColor #edf4f9
    BorderColor #4e7fa0
    FontColor #2a5272
    FontStyle bold
  }
  .cicd {
    BackgroundColor #f5f0fa
    BorderColor #8a6aaa
    FontColor #5a3a7a
    FontStyle bold
  }
  .utility {
    BackgroundColor #edf5ed
    BorderColor #5a8a5a
    FontColor #2a5a2a
    FontStyle bold
  }
}
</style>

* dfetch
** Foundational <<foundational>>
*** init
*** import
*** add
*** check
*** update

** Utilities <<utility>>
*** freeze
*** environment
*** validate

left side

** Patching <<patching>>
*** diff
*** update-patch
*** format-patch

** CI / CD <<cicd>>
*** check\n--jenkins-json
